gIp(){return"Fast, responsive and indexable web apps"},
gIo(){return"Your web presence must feel instant. We build modern web platforms with a strong focus on Core Web Vitals. Our web solutions are designed for ultra-fast loading and full alignment with Google's search algorithms. From complex admin panels to consumer interfaces, we deliver clean code optimized for conversion and fully responsive layouts."},
