gIq(){return"\u2022 Clean code: Clean Architecture for easier maintenance.\n\u2022 Security: Bank-grade security protocols.\n\u2022 Scalability: Systems ready to support from 100 to one million users.\n\u2022 Full-stack support: From UI design to back-end engineering."},
